  <summary date="2005-06-03T19:54:01Z" status="Introduced in House">Requires the Secretary of Agriculture to report annually on the number of required permanent and temporary non-Federal employees for Farm Service Agency (FSA) local offices and the funding levels necessary to support such workforce.

Limits temporary workers to not more than ten percent of all such non-Federal workers in any fiscal year.</summary>
